audio_descriptions.notes:
0: This is a computer generated video that show space shuttle Endeavour in orbit over Earth. It is an example of a video that will be used to recognize people who have sponsored one of the shuttle's thermal tiles to support construction of Endeavour's future home. 

20: Endeavour is floating in space and we zoom into the front edge of the left wing

43: The word Magnopus appears in huge gold lettering, floating in space and illuminated by the sun rising above the Earth  

55: We see Endeavour falling towards Earth as the thermal tiles on the underside of the shuttle glow orange with heat and it moves past the word Magnopus

1:17 It is dark again, and we see Endeavour once again floating in space

result.title: Example Recognition for Team Endeavour Tile Sponsorship Program
result.description: You can join Team Endeavour and help to preserve space shuttle Endeavour's future by sponsoring one of the shuttle's thermal tiles. This video shows an example of how your tile dedication and its location will appear on a 3D model of Space Shuttle Endeavour in an interactive donor display in the Samuel Oschin Air and Space Center - Endeavour's permanent home and the California Science Center's ambitious vision for the future. Visit our website for more information at californiasciencecenter.org.
